  <ABY_BossBar_CalibrationTitle>Boss Bar Calibration</ABY_BossBar_CalibrationTitle>
  <ABY_BossBar_CalibrationDesc>Live adjustment tools for the abyssal boss HUD. Keep a supported boss active on the current map to preview the result in place.</ABY_BossBar_CalibrationDesc>
